sources.title: Oh, Susanna!
sources.description: You can find more information regarding this film on its IMDb page .

metadata.Plot: Fleeing the law, Wolf Benson hops on a train, throws Autry off, and assumes Autry's identity. Still posing as Autry he robs and kills Autry's friend Lee. When Autry is jailed, his friends Frog and the Professor break him out and the three head out to clear him of the murder charge.
metadata.Actors: Gene Autry, Smiley Burnette, Frances Grant
